'''李·保羅·諾瓦克'''（{{lang-en|'''Lee Paul Novak'''}}，{{bd|1988年|9月28日|catIdx=F}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，效力於[[英格蘭足球甲組聯賽|英格蘭足球甲組聯賽]]球會[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯坎索普联]]。

==球員生涯==
===早期===
李·诺瓦克生於[[泰恩河畔纽卡斯尔|泰恩河畔纽卡斯尔]]<ref name="Hugman2010-11 311"/>，自小就是[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]球迷<ref>{{cite news|title=Novak eager for Terriers victory|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/huddersfield_town/8205676.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=17 August 2009}}</ref>。诺瓦克曾效力沃爾森德男生隊的青年軍<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield Town: Lee Novak interview|url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/huddersfield-town-lee-novak-interview-1-2241556|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post|date=15 March 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301161618/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/huddersfield-town-lee-novak-interview-1-2241556|archive-date=2014-03-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但在[[格雷纳足球俱乐部|格雷纳]]展開其職業生涯，2007年8月與隊友轉投[[英格蘭北部超級聯賽|英格蘭北部超級聯賽]][[纽卡斯尔藍星足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔藍星]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Pratt|first=Malcolm|title=New ball game for Star|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Football%3a+New+ball+game+for+Star%3b+UNIBOND+LEAGUE+Division+One+North.-a0167692105|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Evening Chronicle|date=17 August 2007|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130185938/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Football%3a+New+ball+game+for+Star%3b+UNIBOND+LEAGUE+Division+One+North.-a0167692105|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在對奧森特的賽事中大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Bowron|first=Jeff|title=No way back as Novak attacks!|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/No+way+back+as+Novak+attacks!+BLUE+SQUARE+NORTH.-a0188322744|work=Evening Chronicle|accessdate=19 May 2013|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818114846/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/No+way+back+as+Novak+attacks!+BLUE+SQUARE+NORTH.-a0188322744|dead-url=no}}</ref>。效力纽卡斯尔藍星期間曾到訪[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|斯托克港]]和[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯顿]]試腳，但失敗而回<ref name=bluestar>{{cite news|title=Blue Star hit back on Lee Novak|url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/blue-star-hit-back-lee-1449224|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Evening Chronicle|date=6 February 2009|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129063918/https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/blue-star-hit-back-lee-1449224|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年7月，球會應他本人要求掛牌出售，該球季他共打進了27球<ref>{{cite news|last=Pratt|first=Malcolm|title=Star struck by blow as Novak is listed|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Star+struck+by+blow+as+Novak+is+listed.-a0180853155|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Evening Chronicle|date=2 July 2008|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129135838/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Star+struck+by+blow+as+Novak+is+listed.-a0180853155|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他曾考慮轉向澳洲發展，但最終被[[盖茨黑德足球俱乐部|盖茨黑德]]以3,500鎊簽下<ref name=bluestar/><ref name=huddline/>。

===盖茨黑德===
诺瓦克在盖茨黑德的表現出色，11月1日作客對[[海德足球俱乐部|海德]]的比賽中攻進四球，以5-2取勝，其中三球更是三分鐘內完成<ref>{{cite web|title=Novak Record as Gateshead Tame Tigers|url=http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2077/hyde-united-2-5-gateshead|work=gateshead-fc.com|accessdate=19 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814073828/http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2077/hyde-united-2-5-gateshead|archivedate=2012年8月14日}}</ref>。18天後主場對[[林恩国王德足球俱乐部|林恩国王]]的比賽中再次上演帽子戲法，助球隊以3-2取勝<ref>{{cite web|title=Gateshead 3 – 2 Kings Lynn|url=http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2094/gateshead-3-2-kings-lynn|work=gateshead-fc.com|accessdate=19 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814073847/http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2094/gateshead-3-2-kings-lynn|archivedate=2012年8月14日}}</ref>，而他更當選為議會北部聯賽11月最佳球員<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton's Buxton claims accolade|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/7760745.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=2 December 2008}}</ref> 。2009年1月，[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]簽下21場17球的诺瓦克，轉會費為5萬鎊，另有10萬鎊附加條款<ref name=huddline>{{cite news|last=Bowron|first=eff|title=Gateshead's delight as hitman Novak makes all the Huddlines|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Football%3a+Gateshead%27s+delight+as+hitman+Novak+makes+all+the+Huddlines.-a0193033899|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Evening Chronicle|date=3 February 2009|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129052632/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Football%3a+Gateshead%27s+delight+as+hitman+Novak+makes+all+the+Huddlines.-a0193033899|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | date=4 February 2010 | url=http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2615/media-watch-gateshead-receive-terriers-transfer-boost | title=Media Watch – Gateshead receive Terriers transfer boost | publisher=Gateshead F.C. | accessdate=22 March 2010 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100207035545/http://www.gateshead-fc.com/2615/media-watch-gateshead-receive-terriers-transfer-boost | archivedate=2010年2月7日 }}</ref>，而诺瓦克須以外借方式留隊至季末。之後他上場17次打進11球，並助球隊打入晉級附加賽決賽，以1-0擊敗[[AFC泰福特聯|AFC泰福特聯]]晉級至[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]參賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Gateshead 1–0 AFC Telford Utd|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/8038382.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=8 May 2009|archive-date=2009-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511155312/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/8038382.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。诺瓦克以26球成為該季的神射手，並當選為球會年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite news|title=Golden boy Lee Novak scores with top awards|url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/golden-boy-lee-novak-scores-1453514|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=Evening Chronicle|date=28 April 2009|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129111522/https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/golden-boy-lee-novak-scores-1453514|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===哈德斯菲爾德===
2009年7月的季前熱身賽對[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]賽事中，因與[[法布里西奥·科洛奇尼|法布里西奥·科洛奇尼]]打架而受到媒體關注<ref>{{cite news | date=23 July 2009 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8166125.stm | title=FA to look into brawl at friendly | publisher=BBC Sport | accessdate =8 December 2009}}</ref>。他首次替球隊上場是2009年8月8日對[[绍森德足球俱乐部|绍森德]]，以替補入式上場並取得助攻<ref>{{cite news | date=8 August 2009 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8186291.stm | title=Southend 2–2 Huddersfield | publisher=BBC Sport | accessdate =8 August 2009}}</ref>。三天後的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|斯托克港]]首次以先發身份上場並以3-1取勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 3 – 1 Stockport|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/8188028.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=11 August 2009|archive-date=2021-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211225080100/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/8188028.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月18日，他主射[[點球|點球]]進球助球隊7-1大勝[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|布莱顿]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8205231.stm|title=Huddersfield 7–1 Brighton|publisher=BBC Sport|date=18 August 2009|accessdate=21 August 2009|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909011234/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8205231.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後他與拍擋[[乔丹·罗德斯|乔丹·罗德斯]]一起鞏固了自己的先發位置。11月24日至12月12日的四場英甲比賽他都取得進球<ref>{{cite news|title=Swindon 2 – 1 Huddersfield|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8362941.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=24 November 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 3 – 3 Tranmere|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8377317.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=1 December 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/leagueone/leeds/6736854/Leeds-United-2-Huddersfield-Town-2-match-report.html|title=Leeds United 2 Huddersfield Town 2: match report|location=London|work=The Daily Telegraph|first=Will|last=Swanson|date=5 December 2009|accessdate=2014-02-25|archive-date=2010-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530094208/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/leagueone/leeds/6736854/Leeds-United-2-Huddersfield-Town-2-match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 2 – 1 Gillingham|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8398133.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=12 December 2009}}</ref>。3月13日對[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]比賽中因膝傷而退下並缺席之後的五場比賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 1 – 3 Norwich|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8547613.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=13 March 2010}}</ref>。復出後的他在四場比賽中均以替補方式上場，其中三球更是在傷停補時攻進<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 4 – 3 Walsall|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8605999.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=13 April 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Stockport 0 – 6 Huddersfield|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8620745.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=24 April 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 2 – 1 Colchester|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8629896.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=1 May 2010|archive-date=2010-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100503195324/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8629896.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。诺瓦克整個賽季聯賽共上場38次打進12球，球隊以第7名完成並參加晉級附加賽，但被[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米尔沃尔]]淘汰<ref>{{cite news|last=Ashdown|first=John|title=Millwall sink Huddersfield to seal final showdown with Swindon|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/18/millwall-huddesfield-league-one-play-off|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=18 May 2010|archive-date=2011-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110209170531/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/18/millwall-huddesfield-league-one-play-off|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該賽季他在球隊進球球員中排名第三，僅次於16球的乔丹·罗德斯和23球的[[西奧·罗宾逊|西奧·罗宾逊]]。季後他續約至2013年夏天<ref>{{cite news|title=Lee Novak pens Huddersfield Town contract extension|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/huddersfield_town/8786818.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=4 July 2010}}</ref>。

诺瓦克因肌腱拉傷而缺席了2010/11球季中段<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield Town sign Arsenal striker Benik Afobe|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/huddersfield_town/9151783.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=2 November 2010}}</ref>。整個賽季他上場39次但只攻入5球，並參加了晉級附加賽半決賽對[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|伯恩茅斯]]的兩個回合.<ref>{{cite news|last=Ashdown|first=John|title=Huddersfield beat Bournemouth on penalties to reach League One play-off final|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2011/may/18/huddersfield-bournemouth-penalties-match-report|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=18 May 2011|archive-date=2011-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522013310/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2011/may/18/huddersfield-bournemouth-penalties-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在PK大戰中成功射入一球。在決賽中他只是未有上場的替補成員，球隊不敵[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼得伯勒联]]而未能晉級至英冠<ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 0 – 3 Peterborough|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13489373|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=29 May 2011|archive-date=2016-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112094334/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13489373|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011/12球季，诺瓦克並沒有受到任何傷患影響。該球季首次上場是在8月9日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一輪對[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|韦尔港]]，他攻入兩球並以4-2取勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Port Vale 2–4 Huddersfield|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/14368459.stm|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=9 August 2011}}</ref>。雖然球會主教練變為[[西蒙·加利臣|西蒙·加利臣]]，他仍能保持先發位置，全季上次49次攻入17球並助球晉級至英冠。

自球隊晉級至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽]]後，縱使诺瓦克的狀態不穩，但對球隊仍有一些貢獻，尤其是最後兩場聯賽對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]和[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|巴恩斯利]]助球隊保級成功<ref>{{cite news|title=Bristol City 1 – 3 Huddersfield|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22229065|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=27 April 2013|archive-date=2013-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501005030/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22229065|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Huddersfield 2 Barnsley 2: Celebrations all round as both teams safe with Tykes keeper Steele keeping the ball in his area for the last TWO MINUTES to send Posh down|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2319363/Huddersfield-2-Barnsley-2--match-report-Both-teams-safe-incredible-day-drama.html|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=4 May 2013|archive-date=2016-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918074019/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2319363/Huddersfield-2-Barnsley-2--match-report-Both-teams-safe-incredible-day-drama.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。球會自2012年10月便開出一份新合約，但诺瓦克並沒有簽署，並在季後約滿離隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Lee Novak set for Huddersfield Town exit|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22556415|accessdate=19 May 2013|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=16 May 2013|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017154018/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22556415|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
2013年5月21日，诺瓦克追隨前哈德斯菲爾德教練[[李爾·奇勒|李爾·奇勒]]轉投[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite news | language=en | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22615073 | title=Birmingham sign Huddersfield Town striker | publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date=2013-05-21 | accessdate=2015-01-22 | archive-date=2014-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140124155108/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22615073 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。首次代表球會上場是在球季首個賽日對[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]，以1-0落敗<ref name=sb1314>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=51697&season_id=143 |title=Games played by Lee Novak in 2013/2014 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=22 February 2014 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129025507/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=51697&season_id=143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月29日對[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布莱克本流浪者]]比賽中攻入兩球，助球隊以3-2取勝。

